name: Monster of Cookies
description:
HALLOWEEN SPECIAL (burn @ November 1st)

You woke up one day and just could not stop thinking of the sugary delicious taste of fresh homemade chocolate chip cookies, so you decided to bake some. The batter is ready for placement on the baking sheet, and you were able to fit twelve big cookies before running out of space. Relieved you're done with the most of the process, you put the sheet in the oven. You notice the sun shining brightly, and go outside to enjoy it while the cookies are baking. What a beautiful day! Suddenly, your heart jumps as you hear a growl coming from the kitchen. You tread carefully inside, peeking into the kitchen and notice some...blue and cookie-like creature..? You can't believe your eyes. The dough is completely gone too, seems like the eggs had gone bad...
